        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1340586996" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14266195473162830542">I am so grateful that Julie Flygare chose to be transparent about her journey. As a person with Narcolepsy, I felt so isolated and struggled with my self-confidence.<br/><br/>After reading Julie&apos;s story I realize I am one of 3 million who have their lives affected by this invisible chronic condition.<br/><br/>Narcolepsy has cost me a career that I reveled in, a normal social life, and has affected how others view me. I have been lucky enough to find a partner who recognizes when I have hit the wall. He recognizes t</span>
  <span id="freeText14266195473162830542" style="display:none">I am so grateful that Julie Flygare chose to be transparent about her journey. As a person with Narcolepsy, I felt so isolated and struggled with my self-confidence.<br /><br />After reading Julie's story I realize I am one of 3 million who have their lives affected by this invisible chronic condition.<br /><br />Narcolepsy has cost me a career that I reveled in, a normal social life, and has affected how others view me. I have been lucky enough to find a partner who recognizes when I have hit the wall. He recognizes that my frequent naps are not from laziness, but the compelling pull of my sleep attacks.<br /><br />I had never been able to articulate the grainy, burning sensation in my eyes. I almost shouted for not when reading Julie's description of her symptoms.<br /><br />Thank you, Julie Flygare for your crusade to raise awareness of Narcolepsy.<br /><br />I only wish I had read this years ago.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14266195473162830542" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
